\b The Expectations Gap\

\b0 An expectations gap is the result of differences in opinion or perceptions between two or more groups. \
	Reasonableness : Gap between what is expected and what can reasonably be expected to accomplish\
	Performance : Gap between what can reasonably be expected and perceived actual achievements.\
