\b The Research Question\

\b0 How to entrepreneurs, shareholders and managers minimise the loss of value that results from the separation of ownership and control?\
Much prior research assumes that the purpose of the board is shareholder maximisation. This perspective is unlikely to reflect the expectations of a wider group os shareholder and stakeholders in companies. \
